ur-uk-ireland-box-office-1235758875%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fbox-office%2Ftaylor-swift-eras-tour-uk-ireland-box-office-1235758875%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%224%20tips%20for%20small%20businesses%20to%20get%20more%20customer%20reviews%20%E2%80%94%20and%20what%20to%20do%20with%20the%20feedback%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224630%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20of%20the%20three%20cofounders%20of%20Platterful%2C%20with%20Caroline%20Elston%20in%20the%20center.%20The%20three%20are%20around%20a%20table%20with%20a%20charcuterie%20board%20and%20are%20holding%20glasses.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6526ff9b55f52b01b35d00b8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223472%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECaroline%20Elston%2C%20a%20cofounder%20of%20Platterful%2C%20with%20her%20cofounders.%3Cp%3EPlatterful%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EIn%20a%20survey%2C%20nearly%20all%20consumers%20reported%20reading%20reviews%2C%20and%20most%20said%20they%20trusted%20them.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EReviews%20are%20a%20low-cost%20way%20to%20market%20your%20business%20and%20get%20live%20feedback%20from%20customers.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EBusiness%20owners%20should%20respond%20to%20both%20negative%20and%20positive%20reviews.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarketing-for-small-business%5C%22%3EMarketing%20for%20Small%20Business%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20series%20exploring%20the%20basics%20of%20marketing%20strategy%20for%20SBOs%20to%20earn%20new%20customers%20and%20grow%20their%20business.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20someone%20orders%20a%20product%2C%20such%20as%20a%20charcuterie%20kit%2C%20from%20the%20subscription%20service%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatterful.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPlatterful%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20company%20gives%20them%20a%20week%20to%20enjoy%20their%20items.%20Then%2C%20it%20emails%20the%20customer%20asking%20them%20to%20review%20their%20purchase.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20small%20business%20with%20a%20slim%20marketing%20budget%2C%20Caroline%20Elston%2C%20a%20cofounder%20of%20the%20Indiana%20company%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20customer%20reviews%20had%20helped%20Platterful%20raise%20brand%20awareness%20and%20increase%20sales%20since%20it%20launched%20in%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20knew%20if%20others%20shared%20their%20experiences%20publicly%2C%20that%20would%20be%20a%20really%20great%20form%20of%20word-of-mouth%20marketing%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Elston%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlatterful's%20reviews%20are%20posted%20on%20its%20website%20and%20other%20e-commerce%20sites%2C%20including%20Amazon%2C%20Etsy%2C%20and%20Uncommon%20Goods.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.powerreviews.com%2Finsights%2Fpower-of-reviews-survey-2021%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2021%20PowerReviews%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20consumers%2C%20nearly%20all%20respondents%20said%20they%20read%20reviews%20when%20they%20shopped.%20Consumers%20also%20often%20trust%20reviews%20as%20much%20as%20recommendations%20from%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20the%20report%20indicated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20emailing%20customers%20to%20request%20they%20review%20the%20products%20they've%20purchased%2C%20Platterful%20keeps%20a%20flow%20of%20feedback%20coming%20in%2C%20which%20is%20good%20for%20business%2C%20Elston%20said.%20In%20a%202022%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yotpo.com%2Fthe-impact-of-user-generated-content%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYotpo%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20shoppers%2C%2085%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20they%20were%20more%20likely%20to%20buy%20products%20with%20between%2050%20and%20500%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20really%20need%20customers%20to%20leave%20that%20feedback%20so%20we%20can%20build%20from%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20two%20small-business%20owners%20offer%20advice%20for%20collecting%20customer%20reviews%20and%20using%20them%20to%20scale%20their%20businesses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAsk%20for%20reviews%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnn%20Noder%20emails%20clients%20to%20ask%20them%20to%20leave%20reviews%20for%20her%20firm%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pitchpublicrelations.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPitch%20Public%20Relations%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20explains%20how%20much%20she%20values%20the%20reviews%20and%20that%20she%20uses%20them%20for%20new%20business%20development.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTypically%2C%20our%20clients%20are%20more%20than%20willing%20to%20do%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20Noder%2C%20the%20president%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20Phoenix%20company%2C%20told%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reviews%20are%20posted%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Braves%26quot%3B%20section%20of%20the%20company's%20website%20and%20promoted%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20agency%20is%20built%20on%20our%20reputation%2C%20and%20there's%20credibility%20that%20comes%20with%20the%20experience%20and%20testimonials%20that%20come%20directly%20from%20our%20clients%2C%26quot%3B%20Noder%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlatterful's%20review-seeking%20emails%20thank%20customers%20for%20their%20purchases%2C%20mention%20how%20helpful%20the%20reviews%20are%20for%20the%20small%20business%2C%20and%20include%20a%20link%20to%20make%20leaving%20a%20review%20quick%20and%20easy%2C%20Elston%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20posts%20product%20reviews%20on%20social%20media%2C%20which%20encourages%20more%20customers%20to%20write%20reviews%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIncentivize%20customers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yotpo.com%2Fthe-impact-of-user-generated-content%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvey%20by%20Yotpo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20nearly%20half%20of%20online%20shoppers%20said%20they'd%20leave%20a%20review%20if%20offered%20a%20discount%20or%20coupon.%20However%2C%20there%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ftc.gov%2Fbusiness-guidance%2Fresources%2Fsoliciting-paying-online-reviews-guide-marketers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erules%3C%2Fa%3E%20businesses%20must%20follow%2C%20and%20some%20review%20platforms%2C%20including%20Google%2C%20prohibit%20incentivized%20reviews.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20general%2C%20the%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%20says%20you%20can't%20place%20conditions%20on%20review%20incentives%20%E2%80%94%20for%20instance%2C%20offering%20a%20discount%20for%20positive%20reviews%20only.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20its%20initial%20email%20asking%20customers%20for%20a%20review%2C%20Platterful%20sends%20a%20follow-up%20offering%20a%20%2415%20gift%20card%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20review.%20The%20reminders%20and%20incentives%20have%20boosted%20the%20number%20of%20reviews%20the%20company%20gets%2C%20Elston%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ERespond%20to%20feedback%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPlatterful%20responds%20to%20every%20review%20it%20receives%2C%20both%20negative%20and%20positive%2C%20Elston%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20tell%20our%20customers%2C%20'Hey%2C%20we're%20listening%20to%20you%2C%20and%20we're%20taking%20what%20you're%20saying%20very%20seriously.'%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20reviews%20are%20also%20automatically%20sent%20to%20an%20internal%20Slack%20channel%20so%20the%20team%20can%20track%20the%20feedback%20it%20receives%20and%20discuss%20how%20to%20handle%20it%2C%20she%20said.%C2%A0When%20the%20company%20receives%20a%20negative%20review%2C%20it%20contacts%20the%20customer%20to%20resolve%20the%20problem.%20Often%2C%20the%20reviewer%20will%20update%20their%20feedback%20based%20on%20the%20interaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsumers%20expect%20prompt%20responses%20to%20their%20feedback.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brightlocal.com%2Fresearch%2Flocal-consumer-review-survey%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBrightLocal%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20shoppers%2C%2088%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20they%20were%20likely%20to%20use%20a%20business%20that%20responded%20to%20all%20customer%20reviews.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ETake%20action%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EReviews%20can%20provide%20insights%20into%20a%20business%20and%20its%20customers%2C%20Noder%20said.%20Through%20reviews%2C%20she's%20learned%20more%20about%20her%20clients'%20wins%2C%20such%20as%20a%20company%20sharing%20that%20it%20experienced%20a%20sales%20boost%20or%20attracted%20investors%20after%20a%20media%20mention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20ask%20for%20reviews%20and%20respond%20to%20them%2C%20you%20let%20your%20customers%20know%20that%20you%20value%20their%20feedback%2C%20Elston%20said.%20Platterful%20has%20been%20alerted%20to%20customer-service%20issues%20such%20as%20shipping%20delays%20and%20product%20problems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCustomer%20reviews%20are%20your%20live%20focus%20group%20where%20you%20get%20really%20valuable%20feedback%20that%20you%20can%20use%20to%20enhance%20the%20customer%20experience%2C%20enhance%20your%20product%2C%20and%20enhance%20your%20business%20overall%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-small-businesses-get-more-customer-reviews-use-feedback-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697549384000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6526ffb468f1d46f52af195b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-small-businesses-get-more-customer-reviews-use-feedback-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Small%20businesses%20should%20e