ing%20an%20official%20in%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20Office%20(PMO)%20to%20threaten%20the%20top%20executive%20of%20a%20major%20eye%20hospital%20over%20a%20financial%20dispute.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Adil%20Agarwal%2C%20the%20chief%20executive%20of%20Dr%20Agarwal's%20Eye%20Hospital%2C%20had%20won%20an%20arbitration%20battle%20-%20ordered%20by%20the%20high%20court%20-%20to%20receive%20Rs%2016.43%20crore%20from%20two%20Indore-based%20doctors%20who%20had%20allegedly%20cheated%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20and%20Vadodara%20resident%2C%20Mayank%20Tiwari%2C%20sent%20several%20messages%20to%20Dr%20Agarwal%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20two%20doctors%20-%20Dr%20Pranay%20Kumar%20Singh%20and%20Dr%20Sonu%20Verma%20-%20to%20%26quot%3Bsettle%20the%20matter%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20made%20you%20a%20request%20to%20sort%20mutually%20and%20it's%20up%20to%20you%20how%20you%20handle%20the%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20fake%20PMO%20official%20said%20in%20one%20of%20the%20messages%20to%20the%20CEO%20of%20Dr%20Agarwal's%20Eye%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20complaint%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%2C%20the%20PMO%20said%20Mr%20Tiwari%20impersonated%20the%20Director%20of%20government%20advisory%20in%20the%20PMO%20and%20used%20the%20designation%20to%20threaten%20certain%20businesses.%20This%20designation%20and%20the%20person%20do%20not%20exist%2C%20the%20PMO%20said%20in%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Agarwal%20said%20the%20hospital%20and%20the%20two%20Indore-based%20doctors%2C%20who%20ran%20Vinayak%20Netralaya%2C%20signed%20an%20arrangement%20in%20January%202020%20to%20transfer%20the%20entire%20team%20of%20Vinayak%20Netralaya%2C%20including%20the%20two%20doctors%2C%20to%20Dr%20Agarwal's%20Eye%20Hospital.%20Under%20the%20arrangement%2C%20the%20two%20doctors%20had%20also%20agreed%20to%20work%20at%20Dr%20Agarwal's%20Eye%20Hospital.%20Dr%20Agarwal%20said%20the%20hospital%20paid%20Rs%2016.43%20crore%20to%20Dr%20Singh%20and%20Dr%20Verma%20as%20part%20of%20the%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20doctors%2C%20however%2C%20started%20diverting%20patients%20coming%20to%20Dr%20Agarwal's%20Eye%20Hospital%20in%20Indore%20to%20other%20eye%20doctors%20after%20taking%20the%20money%20and%20signing%20the%20arrangement%2C%20Dr%20Agarwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Singh%20and%20Dr%20Verma%20in%20collusion%20with%20other%20doctors%20who%20are%20not%20part%20of%20the%20Dr%20Agarwal's%20Eye%20Hospital%20chain%20also%20started%20a%20competing%20hospital%2C%20ended%20the%20arrangement%20and%20refused%20to%20refund%20the%20money%2C%20Dr%20Agarwal%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20Dr%20Agarwal%20took%20the%20legal%20route%20and%20the%20high%20court%20ordered%20an%20arbitration%2C%20which%20in%20July%202022%20passed%20an%20interim%20inunction%20in%20favour%20of%20Dr%20Aggarwal%20and%20ordered%20the%20two%20Indore-based%20doctors%20to%20deposit%20Rs%2016.43%20crore%20within%20four%20weeks.%20The%20arbitration%20order%20also%20said%20the%20two%20doctors%20cannot%20open%20any%20eye%20hospital%20till%20the%20matter%20with%20Dr%20Agarwal%20is%20settled.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20fake%20PMO%20official%20entered%20the%20scene%20after%20Dr%20Agarwal%20won%20the%20interim%20arbitration%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Agarwal's%20Health%20Care%20Ltd%20is%20supported%20by%20marquee%20investors%2C%20which%20has%20resulted%20in%20the%20company%20opening%20over%20100%20eye%20hospitals%20in%20India%20and%20Africa%20in%20a%20span%20of%20over%20six%20decades%2C%20the%20hospital%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697549040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F7qpef048_dr-agarwal-eye-hospital_625x300_17_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frequest-to-sort-mutually-fake-pmo-official-threatens-ceo-of-dr-agarwal-eye-hospital-4489798%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20man%20from%20Gujarat's%20Vad