E%3Cem%3EFrom%20the%20frontlines%20of%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20war%2C%20NDTV%20brings%20you%20daily%20despatches%20by%20journalist%20Allan%20Sorensen%2C%20Middle%20East%20Correspondent%20for%20Danish%20newspaper%20Kristeligt%20Dagblad%2C%20giving%20insights%20and%20gripping%20first-hand%20accounts%20from%20the%20war-torn%20region.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20arrival%20of%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20in%20Israel%20on%20Wednesday%20was%20confirmed%20late%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20coming%20here%20at%20a%20critical%20moment%20for%20Israel%2C%20for%20the%20region%20and%20for%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20said%20about%20the%20visit%20in%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20press%20in%20the%20Israeli%20city%20of%20Tel%20Aviv.%20Antony%20Blinken%20had%20just%20finished%20an%20unprecedented%20eight-hour%20meeting%20with%20the%20entire%20Israeli%20war%20cabinet%20at%20the%20military%20headquarters%20in%20Tel%20Aviv.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Biden's%20visit%20is%20described%20as%20a%20show%20of%20strong%20support%20to%20Israel%2C%20it%20also%20sends%20a%20warning%20to%20regional%20powers%20such%20as%20Iran%20and%20Hezbollah%20against%20escalating%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20much%20broader%20than%20a%20war%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas.%20The%20US%20President%20sees%20the%20current%20situation%20as%20a%20war%20between%20good%20and%20bad.%20Russia%2C%20Iran%2C%20Hezbollah%20and%20Hamas%20stand%20on%20one%20side%2C%20while%20US%2C%20Europe%20and%20Israel%20stand%20on%20the%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20Amos%20Yadlin%2C%20former%20head%20of%20Israel's%20military%20intelligence%2C%20tells%20Channel%2012.%20He%20adds%20that%20if%20Iran%20and%20Hezbollah%20attack%20Israel%2C%20then%20Israeli%20and%20US%20soldiers%20will%20fight%20shoulder-to-shoulder.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Navy%20has%20dispatched%20two%20aircraft%20carriers%20to%20the%20eastern%20Mediterranean%20Sea%20as%20a%20deterrent%20to%20Israel's%20enemies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20USS%20Dwight%20D%20Eisenhower%20Carrier%20Strike%20Group%20recently%20joined%20the%20USS%20Gerald%20R%20Ford%20group%20in%20the%20Mediterranean%2C%20bringing%20the%20total%20number%20of%20assigned%20American%20warships%20to%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Israeli%20army%20spokesman%20Daniel%20Hagari%20stated%20that%2035%20planes%20with%20ammunition%20are%20en%20route%20to%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20always%20looking%20around%20us%2C%20in%20the%20entire%20Middle%20East.%20The%20IDF%20(Israeli%20Defence%20Force)%20will%20operate%20anywhere%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20to%20fulfil%20Israel's%20security%20aims.%20We%20are%20highly%20prepared%20in%20all%20arenas%2C%26quot%3B%20Daniel%20Hagari%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20The%20Times%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20week%20Israeli%20fighter%20jets%20have%20carried%20out%20attacks%20on%20the%20airports%20of%20Damascus%20and%20Aleppo%20in%20Syria.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJust%20before%20entering%20the%2011th%20day%20of%20fighting%2C%20Abu%20Obeida%20from%20the%20Hamas%20military%20wing%20stated%20that%20the%20group%20is%20holding%20200%20hostage%20in%20Gaza%2C%20and%20another%2050%20are%20being%20held%20by%20other%20Palestinian%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKhaled%20Meshaal%2C%20head%20of%20Hamas'%20diaspora%20office%20in%20Qatar%2C%20said%20Hamas%20demands%20the%20release%20of%206%2C000%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20in%20Israel%20to%20reach%20a%20possible%20prisoner%20swap.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20night%2C%20Hamas%20released%20a%20video%20showing%20Mia%20Shem%2C%20one%20of%20the%20hostages%20in%20Gaza.%20Mia%20Shem%20has%20dual%20Franco-Israeli%20citizenship.%20In%20the%20video%20recording%2C%20she%20says%20she%20is%20being%20treated%20well%20and%20that%20Hamas%20also%20treated%20a%20wound%20on%20her%20hand.%20In%20Israel%2C%20the%20video%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20expected%20part%20of%20psychological%20warfare%2C%20in%20which%20Hamas%20will%20use%20hostages%20to%20raise%20public%20pressure%20on%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Shimrit%20Meir%2C%20former%20adviser%20to%20former%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Naftali%20Bennett%2C%20Hamas%20has%20divided%20the%20hostages%20into%20three%20groups.%20One%20group%20comprises%20Israeli%20soldiers%2C%20the%20second%20has%20Israeli%20children%2C%20women%20and%20elders%2C%20while%20the%20third%20group%20is%20made%20up%20of%20Israelis%20with%20dual%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20border%20between%20Egypt%20and%20Gaza%2C%20the%20situation%20escalated%20dramatically%20on%20Monday%20when%20Israeli%20jets%20hit%20the%20area%20for%20a%20fourth%20time%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20latest%20fighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Rafah%20border%20between%20Gaza%20and%20Egypt%20remains%20closed%20while%20thousands%20of%20Palestinians%20wait%20in%20the%20border%20area.%20The%20massive%20and%20ongoing%20Israeli%20bombardment%20of%20Gaza%20continues%20and%20every%20day%2C%20more%20Palestinians%20are%20seeking%20shelter%20by%20moving%20to%20south%20Gaza%2C%20as%20requested%20by%20the%20Israeli%20army.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20Israeli%20blockade%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Rafah%20border%20remains%20closed%20escalates%20the%20humanitarian%20crisis%20inside%20Gaza%20by%20the%20hour%20and%20draws%20the%20city%20closer%20to%20a%20total%20collapse.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEgypt%20and%20the%20US%20made%20a%20request%20to%20Israel%20on%20Monday%20to%20allow%20a%20convoy%20of%20trucks%20with%20humanitarian%20aid%20to%20cross%20from%20Egypt%20into%20Gaza.%20Israel%20rejected%20this%20request%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20spiralling%20humanitarian%20crisis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20UN%20personnel%20inside%20Gaza%2C%20hospitals%20are%20running%20out%20of%20medicine%20and%20fuel.%20Water%20is%20scarce%20and%20no%20food%20products%20have%20been%20delivered%20since%20the%20middle%20of%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20European%20Union%20said%20on%20Monday%20it%20would%20launch%20a%20humanitarian%20air%20bridge%20of%20%26quot%3Bseveral%20flights%26quot%3B%20to%20Egypt%20with%20aid%20to%20the%20population%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20two%20flights%20will%20take%20place%20this%20week%2C%20carrying%20humanitarian%20cargo%20from%20UNICEF%2C%20including%20shelter%20items%2C%20medicines%20and%20hygiene%20kits%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20EU%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20al-Arabiya%20channel%2C%20some%20100%20trucks%20are%20already%20waiting%20on%20the%20Egyptian%20border%20for%20the%20green%20light%20to%20cross%20the%20border%20into%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20NPR%2C%20John%20Kirby%2C%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20US%20National%20Security%20Council%2C%20emphasized%20the%20importance%20of%20avoiding%20a%20humanitarian%20disaster%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20that%20humanitarian%20assistance%20should%20absolutely%20continue%20to%20flow%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza.%20They%20have%20every%20right%20to%20expect%20food%2C%20water%20and%20medicine.%20And%20the%20United%20States%20is%20going%20to%20continue%20to%20work%20with%20our%20partners%20to%20that%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Israel's%20border%20to%20Lebanon%20tension%20remains%20high.%20After%20a%20relatively%20quiet%20beginning%20to%20the%20day%2C%20the%20Hezbollah%20attacked%20Israeli%20positions%20on%20Monday%20evening%20with%20at%20least%20five%20anti-tank%20missiles.%20No%20one%20was%20hurt%20in%20the%20attacks%2C%20but%20later%20in%20the%20evening%20Israeli%20jets%20overflying%20the%20city%20of%20Haifa%20in%20low%20altitude%20hit%20targets%20inside%20Lebanon.%20Among%20them%20were%20four%20Hezbollah%20fighters%20who%20tried%20to%20cross%20the%20border%20between%20Lebanon%20and%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20televised%20interview%20with%20Iranian%20state%20TV%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20country's%20Foreign%20Minister%20Hossein%20Amir%20Abdollahian%20revealed%20that%20Iran%20considers%20pre-emptive%20action%20if%20Israel%20continues%20to%20attack%20Gaza.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%2C%20Hizbullah%20and%20Iran%20are%20part%20of%20the%20so-called%20axis%20of%20resistance%20against%20Israel.%20The%20comments%20of%20Hossein%20Amir%20Abdollahian%20come%20after%20his%20return%20from%20regional%20meetings%20with%20representatives%20from%20these%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPre-emptive%20action%20is%20possible%20in%20the%20coming%20few%20hours%20because%20the%20leaders%20(of%20the%20resistance%20axis)%20will%20naturally%20not%20allow%20the%20Zionist%20regime%20to%20do%20whatever%20it%20wants%20in%20Gaza%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20war%20crimes%20against%20the%20Palestinians%20are%20not%20immediately%20stopped%2C%20other%20multiple%20fronts%20will%20open%20and%20this%20is%20inevitable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Allan%20Sorensen%20is%20the%20Middle%20East%20correspondent%20for%20the%20Danish%20daily%20newspaper%20Kristeligt%20Dagblad.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697548440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F8ecg9ncg_daily-despatch_625x300_17_October_23.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdaily-despatch-bidens-visit-to-israel-hamas-hostage-video-gaza-crisis-4489748%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Although%20Biden's%20visit%20is%20described%20as%20a%20show%20of%20strong%20support%20to%20Israel%2C%20it%20also%20sends%20a%20warning%20to%20regional%20powers%20such%20as%20Iran%20and%20Hezbollah%20against%20escalating%20the%20situation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdail