20have%20publicly%20called%20on%20Israel%20to%20protect%20noncombatants%20as%20it%20prepares%20for%20a%20massive%20ground%20invasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20officials%20can't%20believe%20it.%20They%20have%20spent%20every%20day%20since%20the%20attacks%20bringing%20foreign%20leaders%20and%20journalists%20to%20the%20unbearably%20grim%20sites%20of%20the%20killing%2C%20gathering%20testimonies%20from%20survivors%20and%20splicing%20together%20video%20of%20gruesome%20beheadings%20and%20eye-gougings%20recorded%20-%20often%20gleefully%20-%20by%20the%20perpetrators.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20aim%20of%20these%20presentations%20is%20to%20get%20the%20world%20to%20agree%20that%20Israel%20now%20has%20not%20only%20a%20license%20to%20destroy%20Hamas%20-%20designated%20a%20terrorist%20organization%20by%20the%20US%20and%20European%20Union%20-%20but%20a%20collective%20responsibility%20to%20do%20so%2C%20just%20as%20the%20US%20won%20international%20support%20after%20the%20September%2011%20attacks%20to%20eradicate%20Al-Qaeda%20and%20later%20against%20ISIS.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20put%20up%20fliers%20and%20signs%20of%20missing%20persons%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20Israel%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22People%20put%20up%20fliers%20and%20signs%20of%20missing%20persons%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20Israel%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F85saaof8_missing-persons-posters-bloomberg_625x300_17_October_23.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EPeople%20put%20up%20fliers%20and%20signs%20of%20missing%20persons%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20Israel%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20no%20two%20sides%20to%20this%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lior%20Haiat%2C%20spokesman%20for%20Israel's%20Foreign%20Ministry%20in%20a%20Zoom%20presentation%20that%20included%20two%20survivors%20on%20Monday.%20%26quot%3BIf%20someone%20is%20not%20standing%20with%20us%20today%2C%20he%20is%20standing%20with%20monsters%20who%20murder%20babies%20and%20old%20people.%20If%20you%20are%20not%20standing%20against%20terror%2C%20you%20are%20part%20of%20terror.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Israel%2C%20the%20mobilization%20of%20360%2C000%20soldiers%20and%20demand%20that%201.1%20million%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20move%20south%20within%2024%20hours%20as%20it%20pounded%20the%20area%20from%20the%20air%20count%20as%20justified%20responses%20to%20unspeakable%20acts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20me%20tell%20you%2C%20Mr.%20Secretary%2C%20this%20will%20be%20a%20long%20war%2C%20the%20price%20will%20be%20high%2C%26quot%3B%20Israeli%20Defense%20Minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%20warned%20Blinken%20Monday.%20%26quot%3BBut%20we%20are%20going%20to%20win%20for%20Israel%20and%20the%20Jewish%20people%2C%20and%20for%20the%20values%20that%20both%20countries%20believe%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20elsewhere%2C%20Israel's%20preparations%20are%20fueling%20more%20alarm%20than%20resolve.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20has%20publicly%20sided%20with%20Israel's%20view%20that%20Hamas%20should%20be%20eliminated%20entirely%2C%20he's%20repeatedly%20called%20on%20the%20government%20to%20limit%20civilian%20casualties.%20%26quot%3BThe%20overwhelming%20majority%20of%20Palestinians%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20Hamas%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUK%20Foreign%20Secretary%20James%20Cleverly%20told%20Sky%20News%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20in%20Israel's%20interest%20to%20avoid%20civilian%20casualties%20and%20Palestinian%20casualties%2C%20because%20Hamas%20clearly%20wants%20to%20turn%20this%20into%20a%20wider%20Arab-Israeli%20war%2C%20or%20indeed%20a%20war%20between%20the%20Muslim%20world%20and%20the%20wider%20world.%20And%20none%20of%20us%2C%20including%20Israel%2C%20want%20that%20to%20be%20the%20case.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20Hamas%20isn't%20seen%20as%20a%20global%20terror%20force%20the%20way%20ISIS%20and%20Al-Qaeda%20were.%20Instead%2C%20it's%20often%20portrayed%20as%20an%20awful%20product%20of%20decades%20of%20oppression%20by%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOfficials%20across%20the%20region%20-%20in%20Kuwait%2C%20Bahrain%2C%20Egypt%2C%20Jordan%2C%20and%20elsewhere%20-%20say%20their%20populations%20are%20restive%20as%20they%20watch%20Israel%20pound%20Gaza.%20Their%20citizens%20display%20a%20high%20degree%20of%20support%20for%20Hamas%2C%20making%20it%20hard%20for%20them%20to%20even%20condemn%20the%20October%207%20attacks.%20They%20are%20pressuring%20the%20US%20for%20humanitarian%20aid%20to%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20officials%20chafe%20at%20what%20they%20see%20as%20hypocritical%20lecturing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20Americans%20went%20to%20Fallujah%20after%209%2F11%2C%20they%20didn't%20ask%20questions%20about%20the%20humanitarian%20needs%20of%20Fallujah%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Yaakov%20Amidror%2C%20who%20was%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu's%20national%20security%20adviser%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20speaking%20to%20foreign%20journalists.%20%26quot%3BThe%20best%20example%20is%20the%20Second%20World%20War%20in%20which%20the%20whole%20free%20world%20fought%20against%20German%20Nazis%2C%20and%20no%20one%20asked%20about%20the%20humanitarian%20needs%20of%20the%20enemy.%20It's%20a%20war%20against%20an%20enemy%20state.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Israel%2C%20there%20is%20a%20sense%20that%20no%20matter%20what%20has%20happened%20before%20-%20settlement%20building%2C%20military%20incursions%20-%20history%20turned%20a%20new%20page%20on%20October%207%20because%20of%20the%20level%20of%20savagery%20on%20display.%20The%20impact%20has%20been%20deeply%20personal%20in%20a%20small%20country%20where%20almost%20no%20one%20has%20been%20unaffected%2C%20and%20where%20many%20come%20from%20countries%20of%20pogroms%20and%20Holocaust.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20on%20Monday%20brought%20a%20dozen%20foreign%20correspondents%20to%20see%20a%2042-minute%20compilation%20of%20the%20horrors%20of%20October%207%2C%20showing%20attackers%20stopping%20cars%20and%20shooting%20passengers%2C%20axing%20a%20dead%20body%2C%20burning%20a%20house%2C%20and%20resting%20to%20drink%20water%20on%20a%20porch.%20The%20military's%20chief%20spokesman%2C%20Rear%20Admiral%20Daniel%20Hagari%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20see%20this%20as%20a%20war%20against%20humanity%2C%20not%20just%20Israel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20visits%20by%20German%20Chancellor%20Olaf%20Scholz%20and%20probably%20by%20Biden%20are%20likely%20to%20delay%20Israel's%20invasion%20of%20Gaza.%20The%20more%20time%20passes%2C%20the%20wider%20the%20gap%20is%20likely%20to%20grow%20between%20the%20view%20held%20firmly%20by%20Israel%20and%20much%20of%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697546580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F7ndvfk08_israelgaza-war-reuters_625x300_17_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgaza-deaths-hurting-israels-attempt-to-cast-hamas-as-isis-4489608%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20met%20Saudi%20Crown%20Prince%20Mohammed%20bin%20Salman%20in%20Riyadh%20Sunday%2C%20both%20posted%20a%20similar%20photo%20-%20but%20with%20contrasting%20descriptions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgaza-deaths-hurting-israels-attempt-to-cast-hamas-as-isis-4489608%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgaza-deaths-hurting-israels-attempt-to-cast-hamas-as-isis-4489608%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgaza-deaths-hurtin