ng%20carried%20out%2C%20there%20were%20many%20Gazans%20of%20goodwill%2C%20many%20Palestinians%20of%20good%20conscience%20who%20abhor%20violence%20as%20do%20you%2C%20as%20do%20I%2C%20who%20abhor%20the%20targeting%20of%20civilians.%20As%20do%20you.%20As%20do%20I.%20Who%20was%20able%20to%20breathe.%20They%20were%20able%20to%20breathe%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20years.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20crowd%20then%20chanted%2C%20''From%20the%20river%20to%20the%20sea%2C%20Palestine%20will%20be%20free.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EFor%20full%20context%2C%20here%20is%20the%20entire%20video%20of%20Cornell%20University%20Professor%20Russell%20Rickford%20speaking%20about%20Hamas%20terrorist%20attacks.%20Thanks%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnnn_Netanel_nnn%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40nnn_Netanel_nnn%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20sharing.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F6ApgIq38BR%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F6ApgIq38BR%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Sam%20Aberman%20(%40samaberman)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsamaberman%2Fstatus%2F1714081199050662092%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2017%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EMany%20on%20social%20media%20criticised%20his%20statements%2C%20calling%20them%20''abhorrent''.%20One%20user%20said%2C%20''I%20watched%20the%20first%20clip%20and%20thought%20maybe%20something%20was%20taken%20out%20of%20context.%20Sad%20to%20see%20that%20it%20was%20not%20out%20of%20context.%20Abhorrent.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20commented%2C%20''Jesus.%20It%20does%20not%20sound%20like%20he%20abhor%20violence%20all%20that%20much.''%20A%20third%2C%20''This%20is%20sickening%2C%20disgusting%2C%20disappointing.''%20A%20fourth%20added%2C%20''It's%20breathtaking%20how%20ideologists%20love%20principles%20and%20societal%20power%20mechanisms%20more%20than%20they%20love%20life%20and%20people.%20And%2C%20how%20they%20fail%20to%20understand%20even%20explicit%20motivations%20for%20terror%20that%20does%20not%20fit%20their%20own%20framework%20of%20power%20politics.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20Hamas'%20weekend%20attack%20on%20Israel%2C%20Israel%20has%20bombarded%20and%20laid%20siege%20to%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20controlled%20by%20Hamas%2C%20and%20plans%20a%20ground%20invasion.%20Amid%20the%20growing%20conflict%2C%20tensions%20between%20students%20on%20opposite%20sides%20of%20the%20issue%20have%20boiled%20over%20on%20some%20U.S.%20college%20campuses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStatements%20by%20student%20groups%20supporting%20Palestinians%20have%20prompted%20outrage%20and%20fear%20among%20Jews%20and%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20wider%20rebuke%20from%20public%20officials%20and%20corporations.%20There%20have%20been%20reports%20of%20harassment%20and%20assaults%20of%20both%20pro-Israel%20and%20pro-Palestinian%20students%2C%20deepening%20grief%20and%20putting%20students%20of%20all%20political%20stripes%20on%20high%20alert.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%C2%A0Idan%20Ofer%2C%20an%20Israeli%20shipping%20tycoon%20with%20a%20multi-billion-dollar%20fortune%2C%20and%20his%20wife%20Batia%20have%20stepped%20down%20from%20their%20roles%20as%20board%20members%20at%20Harvard's%20Kennedy%20School.%20Their%20resignation%20came%20in%20protest%20of%20what%20they%20perceive%20as%20the%20university's%20lukewarm%20response%20to%20a%20letter%20from%20student%20organizations.%20The%20letter%20placed%20full%20blame%20on%20the%20Israeli%20government%20for%20the%20recent%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20operatives%2C%20which%20killed%20over%201%2C000%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697542740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F4l6nt3eo_cornell-university-professor_625x300_17_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-palestine-conflict-us-professor-calls-hamas-attacks-exhilarating-and-energising-sl