%20Force%20neutralised%20the%20National%20Security's%20Commander%20of%20Hamas%2C%20identified%20as%20Muetaz%20Eid.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMerad%20Abu%20Merad%2C%20a%20Hamas%20commander%20who%20is%20said%20to%20have%20led%20the%20October%207%20attack%20on%20Israel%2C%20was%20also%20killed%20by%20Israel%20on%20Saturday%2C%20its%20military%20said.%20Merad%20was%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Hamas%20aerial%20system.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20IDF%20also%20struck%20over%20one%20hundred%20military%20targets%20located%20in%20Zaytun%2C%20Khan%20Yunis%2C%20and%20west%20Jabaliya.%20These%20strikes%20impacted%20the%20capabilities%20of%20the%20Hamas%20terrorist%20organization%2C%20by%20targeting%20its%20operational%20command%20centers%2C%20military%20compounds%2C%20dozens%20of%20launchers%2C%20anti-tank%20missile%20launch%20posts%2C%20and%20observation%20posts.%20Furthermore%2C%20operational%20command%20centers%20belonging%20to%20the%20Islamic%20Jihad%20terrorist%20organization%20were%20struck%2C''%20the%20IDF%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20troops%20also%20killed%20four%20militants%20attempting%20to%20infiltrate%20from%20Lebanon%2C%20the%20army%20said%20Tuesday%2C%20as%20tensions%20run%20high%20along%20the%20border%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%20Earlier%20the%20army%20said%20it%20had%20carried%20out%20strikes%20overnight%20on%20Hezbollah%20%26quot%3Bterrorist%26quot%3B%20targets%20inside%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20over%20one%20million%20people%20in%20Gaza%20have%20been%20displaced%20as%20Israeli%20troops%20now%20wait%20for%20a%20political%20go-ahead%20to%20launch%20a%20ground%20invasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697539860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fd0fisve8_hamas-operatives_625x300_17_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpics-of-top-hamas-operatives-killed-by-israel-released-4489007%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20list