deo%20he%20released%20after%20taking%20charge%20of%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3EDTNext%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Palanivel%20said%20that%20Veeramuthuvel%20is%20the%20first%20graduate%20in%20their%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20Veeramuthuvel%E2%80%99s%20time%20pursuing%20a%20diploma%20in%20mechanical%20engineering%20at%20a%20polytechnic%20college%20that%20he%20discovered%20his%20first%20passion.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20pursuing%20the%20diploma%2C%20I%20got%20interested%20in%20engineering.%20I%20secured%2090%20percent%20marks%20in%20all%20papers%20and%20got%20an%20engineering%20seat%20on%20merit%20in%20the%20Shri%20Sai%20Ram%20Engineering%20College%20in%20Chennai%20for%20a%20Bachelor%20of%20Engineering%20course%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETransforming%20from%20an%20average%20student%2C%20he%20began%20excelling%20in%20engineering.%20From%20then%20on%2C%20he%20consistently%20ranked%20first%20or%20second%20in%20every%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reason%20was%20not%20that%20I%20was%20studying%20all%20the%20time.%20But%20when%20I%20was%20engaged%20with%20my%20studies%2C%20I%20would%20try%20to%20study%20with%20100%20percent%20focus%20and%20make%20an%20effort%20to%20understand%20everything%20that%20I%20studied.%20This%20is%20the%20reason%20I%20was%20able%20to%20secure%20good%20marks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20secured%20admission%20to%20the%20then%20REC%2C%20which%20is%20today%20called%20NIT%20Trichy%2C%20for%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20engineering%2C%20in%20which%20he%20also%20excelled%20with%20a%209.17%20CGPA.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Hard%20work%20will%20never%20go%20unrewarded%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EChandrayaan-3%20Mission%3A%3Cbr%3E%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3Vikram%20soft-landed%20on%20%F0%9F%8C%96%2C%20ag