e%20team%2C%20successfully%20launching%20three%20of%20them.%20With%20a%20team%20of%20young%20scientists%2C%20all%20under%20the%20age%20of%2040%2C%20they%20achieved%20this%20feat%20in%20just%20nine%20months%2C%20propelling%20Veeramuthuvel%20to%20the%20pinnacle%20of%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%2015%20to%2020%20%5Bscientists%5D%20and%20they%20came%20up%20with%20a%20bus%20configuration%20for%20the%20project%2C%20which%20was%20launched%20around%202017.%20This%20was%20the%20time%20we%20saw%20his%20leadership%20qualities%20and%20that%20helped%20him%20emerge%20as%20the%20project%20director%20after%20the%20failure%20of%20Chandrayaan-2%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20former%20ISRO%20scientist%20and%20satellite%20centre%20director%20M%20Annadurai%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20that%2C%20Veeramuthuvel%20was%20appointed%20as%20an%20associate%20project%20director%20for%20the%20Chandrayaan-2%20mission%20and%20later%20promoted%20to%20the%20role%20of%20project%20director%20for%20Chandrayaan-3%2C%20where%20he%20led%20a%20substantial%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324699%2Fawais-ahmed-founded-space-startup-pixxel-hyperspectral-satellite-launch-hyperloop-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20humble%20scientist%20%3C%2Fa%3Esays%20that%20one%20must%20make%20use%20of%20their%20opportunities%20well%20to%20reach%20the%20top.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20simple%20person.%20If%20I%20am%20able%20to%20achieve%20these%20things%20and%20reach%20this%20level%2C%20everyone%20else%20can%20do%20it%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20of%20us%20get%20opportunities%3B%20it%20is%20about%20how%20we%20use%20them.%20Self-discipline%2C%20100%20percent%20involvement%20without%20any%20expectation%2C%20hard%20work%2C%20and%20our%20uniqueness%20will%20definitely%20bring%20success.%20Hard%20work%20will%20never%20go%20unrewarded%2C%E2%80%9D%20remarked%20Veeramuthuvel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESources%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dtnext.in%2Fnews%2Ftamilnadu%2Faverage-student-spiritual-says-dad-on-veeramuthuvel-732016%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Average%20student%2C%20spiritual%2C%20says%20dad%20on%20Veeramuthuvel%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20K%20Karthikeyan%20for%20DT%20Next%2C%20Published%20on%2025%20August%202023%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697119303000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D332112%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20Chandrayaan%203%2C%20Project%20Director%20P%20Veeramuthuvel%20recently%20explained%20the%20roadmap%20for%20Gaganyaan%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20manned%20mission%20to%20space.%20His%20journey%20from%20a%20Tamil%20Nadu%20village%20to%20ISRO%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20power%20of%20hard%20work.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332112%2Fisro-chandrayaan-3-project-director-p-veeramuthuvel-gaganyaan-tamil-nadu%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Auto%20Workers%20Strike%20Hits%20Ford's%20Kentucky%20Truck%20Plant%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22The%20union%20said%20it%20launched%20the%20surprise%20strike%20after%20failing%20to%20make%20progress%20in%20negotiations%20with%20the%20iconic%20automaker.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697067122000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F652727581f000079001ba741.jpeg%3Fcache%3Dyiatlnhj5d%26ops%3D224_126%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fauto-workers-strike-hits-fords-kentucky-truck-plant_n_6527250ce4b09f4b8d42ee8a%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20union%20said%20it%20launched%20the%20surprise%20strike%20after%20failing%20to%20make%20progress%20in%20negotiations%20with%20the%20ico